---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于 | 军舰日志">
  <section class="py-16 px-8 bg-white border-b border-[var(--border)]">
    <div class="max-w-[950px] mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--text-secondary)] no-underline text-sm mb-8 transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[var(--accent)]">
        <span>←</span>
        返回首页
      </a>
      <h1 class="font-['Newsreader',_Georgia,_serif] text-[3.5rem] font-semibold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.03em] mb-2 animate-fade-in-up">
        关于
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[950px] mx-auto">
      <div class="prose animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        <p>欢迎来到军舰日志！</p>

        <p>这是一个务实程序员的技术博客，专注于分享编程、系统管理、人工智能等领域的知识和经验。</p>

        <h2>联系方式</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/wang-junjian">wang-junjian</a></li>
          <li>Email: wang-junjian@qq.com</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
